entries.yarrock: A root derived spice with strong mind enhancing properties.
entries.won_won: A greasy dinner pastry common to the Wookiee diet.
entries.wheel_of_cheese: A soft wheel of fresh cheese.
entries.wedding_cake: A magnificent cake to celebrate the occasion of marriage.
entries.wastril_bread: A crumbly bread with fruit flavorings common on Corellia.
entries.veronian_berry_wine: A sweet berry wine with light flavors.  A great dessert wine.
entries.vercupti_eff: Grants enhanced health, action, and mind.
entries.vercupti: An unidentifiable dish popularized by Dexter Jettster in the years following the Battle of Naboo.
entries.veghash: A vegetable mush often served as a side dish in cantinas.
entries.vegetarian_dish: A no-meat approach to nutrition, this vegetarian dish looks delicious.
entries.vegeparsine: A high quality version of veghash favored by the rich.
entries.vayerbok: A vegetable based beer that is as thick as it is green.
entries.vasarian_brandy_eff: Grants enhanced mind, focus, and willpower.
entries.vasarian_brandy: A rare brandy made from the fruit and berries of Talus.
entries.vagnerian_canape: A sweet pastry often served at formal dinners.
entries.tssolok: T'ssolok is an intense Twi'lek liquor that is always served in a decorative decanter.  While the standing flavor of T'ssolok is not particularly good, the aftertaste is delicious.
entries.triple_meat_wrap: A tasty Triple Meat Wrap, three meats wrapped in a thin bit of leathery hide.
entries.trimpian: Sliced meat served in a seasoned miasra sauce.
entries.tray_of_pastries: An assortment of soft pastries on a tray.
entries.tray_of_cookies: A tray of soft, fresh cookies.
entries.travel_biscuits: Hearty biscuits full of nutrients for long trips.
entries.tranna_nougat_cream: A sweet candy that is extremely difficult to make.  It is favored by the rich and powerful.
entries.tilla_tiil: A sparkling Twi'lek wine notable for the triple carbonation and filtering process used in its creation.
entries.thruster_head: Thruster Head is the street name for an intense synaptic enhancement stim.  When injected Thruster Head multiplies the user's mental capabilities ten fold, at the cost of increased anxiety and extreme nausea.
entries.thakitillo: A curdled dish known for the tangy explosion of flavor experienced when mashed against the roof of the mouth.
entries.terratta: A dish made from hide strips smothered in oil and milk.
entries.teltier_noodles: A vegetable and noodle dish served lukewarm.  The noodles are usually mushy and only slightly cooked.
entries.tatooine_sunburn: Native to the Mos Eisley Cantina, Tatooine Sunburn is a rough drink that will put you under the table quick...which is exactly where most thieves want you.
entries.synthsteak: A tasty fortified steak substitute designed to withstand long space travel.
entries.sweetblossom: A thick fluid made from the Sweetblossom with strong sedative properties.  Sometimes used as a field anaesthetic or truth serum.
entries.sullustan_gin: A common form of gin distilled by the Sullustan race.  This gin has a light flavor and may be used as a base for other recipes requiring alcohol.
entries.stewed_gwouch: A highly nutritional food...the flavor leaves something to be desired.
entries.starshine_surprise: A strong alcoholic beverage infused with reactive gas.  Often lit on fire before consumed.
entries.spiced_tea: A beverage consisting of water flavored by strong spices.
entries.spice_up: You are enhanced by the positive effects of the spice.
entries.spice_down: You are suffering from the downer effects of the spice.
entries.smugglers_delight: A sweet pastry with a hollow center.
entries.small_avian: A small chunk of avian meat.
entries.skannbult_likker: A rare beverage distilled from special types of corn and wheat.
entries.shot: A shot, filled to the brim.
entries.shadowpaw: Shadowpaw is the name of the powder that remains when the Edorian Itassi root is ground up.  This powder was originally used by the native Ewok race in spiritual ceremonies via a long bone pipe, but has since found a place in various cantinas and criminal dives.
entries.sedative_h4b: A medical sedative used on battle fields to treat traumatic injuries.  H4b's strong depressive properties result in it often being used for recreational purposes.
entries.scrimpi: A meat dish common to cantina menus.
entries.scramjet: is the rough street name for a body building food additive.  Due to its distorting and potentially harmful effects on humanoid biology, scramjet has been outlawed on Imperial worlds.
entries.ryshcate: A dark brown Corellian sweetbread served on birthdays.
entries.ruby_bliel: A non-alcoholic fruit drink favored by children.
entries.rations: Military quality rations often found on large starliners.
entries.ramorrean_capanata: A popular pasta that tastes best when served with seafood.
entries.rakririan_burnout_sauce: An extremely spicy sauce!  Be careful!
entries.pyrepenol: A concentrated pyrepenol pill.  When consumed it results in heightened physical strength.
entries.pyollian_cake: Extra sweet gooey cake made with carbosyrup.
entries.puk: A vegetable commonly grown in private hydroponics bays.
entries.puffcake: A small dessert pastry popular with children.
entries.pkneb: A sweet meat rolled in crushed bone and caramelized.
entries.pizza: A steaming hot pizza, topped with fresh cheese, baked meats, and assorted toppings.
entries.pikatta_pie: A rich and thick pie thought to have been invented by Baron Hodor of Teyr.
entries.patot_panak: A type of flatbread served with meat and seasoning.
entries.ormachek: A healthy wrapped meal favored by Mon Calamari for its memory enhancing properties.
entries.neutron_pixey: A calming hallucinogen of unknown alien origin, Neutron Pixie is usually ingested with a light fruit flavoring to increase palatability.
entries.nanana_twist: A candy made with inert gas and berry fruit.
entries.muon_gold: A subatomic reactant that results in intense mental clarity and focus.  Banned by Imperial authorities due to its degenerative effect on neural pathways.
entries.meaty_nuggets: Dried nuggets of meat, cooked to perfection, and made as an snack food.
entries.meatlump: A processed and compressed meat hunk used in space station food stores.
entries.meat_skewer: A juicy skewer of meat, vegetables, and fruit.
entries.meat_loaf: A generous cut of meat loaf.
entries.marinade: A mixture of vinegar, oil, spices and herbs.
entries.mandalorian_wine: A strong, bitter wine. This drink was made popular in the years following the Mandalorian Wars.
entries.large_avian: A large chunk of avian meat.
entries.kylessian_fruit_distillate: An alcohol stock distilled from fruits.  This can be used as a component in any recipe requiring alcohol.  In general, Kylessian Fruit Distillate has a higher quality than Sullustan Gin.
entries.kiwik_clusjo_swirl: An unusual mixture of fruits, served creamed.
entries.kanali_wafers: A sugary pastry pressed flat and served chilled.
entries.jerky: Some meaty Jerky, dried to last longer but remaining very tasty.
entries.jawa_beer: A rough travel beer brewed from fermented grains and bantha hide.
entries.jaar: A sweet drink of fermented milk and fruit, favored by Wookiees.
entries.ithorian_mist: A type of whiskey favored by the Ithorian race.
entries.ice_blaster: A warming alcoholic beverage made from Sullustan Gin.
entries.havla: A spiced toast popular with nobility.
entries.gunjack: A highly concentrated methylpenatox and glucose based chemical cocktail that grants the user intense physical strength while decreasing fine motor control and the ability to reason.
entries.grey_gabaki: A plant named for its drab color when dried, Grey Gabaki gives off a light and relaxing smoke when burned.  It is commonly used in cantinas, but some merchants also burn it to make store fronts a more relaxing environment for customers.
entries.gralinyn_juice: A fermented Wookiee beverage.  Light by Wookiee standards.
entries.gorrnar: A frozen dessert favored by Wookiees.
entries.giggledust: An all natural dust that is inhaled to create a sense of euphoria and alertness.
entries.garrmorl_eff: Grants enhanced health, strength, and constitution.
entries.garrmorl: Another rough Wookiee beverage made from dried bone and hide mixed with alcohol stock.
entries.fried_endwa: A tasty fried meal common on Corellia.
entries.force_melon: This fruit was picked from the Aurilian plant, a notoriously fickle and difficult plant to grow to fruition. The nectar from this fruit provides a vitalizing rush to those that consume it.
entries.food_basket: A basket of fruits and other food.
entries.food_additive_medium: A medium food additive.  This can be used in a Medium or Heavy additive slot during food crafting.
entries.food_additive_light: A light food additive.  This can be used in a Light, Medium, or Heavy additive slot during food crafting.
entries.food_additive_heavy: A heavy food additive.  This can only be used in a Heavy additive slot during food crafting.
entries.flameout: A strange reactive beverage.  It burns the tongue while at the same time freezes the throat.
entries.fire_stew: A spicy stew flavored with puk and desert flowers.
entries.felbar: A baked dessert made with flower fruit.
entries.exo_protein_wafers: Enhanced protein wafers used by space farers during long trips.
entries.elshandruu_pica_thundercloud: This drink is probably the strongest in the galaxy.  Highly dangerous.
entries.dweezel: A gooey pastry common to Mos Espa.  Invented by the culinary genius Professor Umlaut.
entries.dustcrepe: A light crepe native to Tatooine.
entries.durindfire: A rare alcoholic beverage that lights up with a phosphorescent glow when exposed to oxygen.
entries.droid_lube: Zypolene Droid Lubricant was once used as a very common homemade joint and servo lubricant for robot servants.  After medical studies suggested the substance was the cause of cellular decay among various races, the use of zypolene decreased.  It has a burning, stimulating effect when rubbed across open skin.
entries.drink_nectar: A delicious blend of exotic plant nectars, fruit juices and mineral waters.
entries.double_dip_outer_rim_rumdrop: Native to the Spirited Spirits shop on Cularin, this strong mixed drink is made from a wide range of alcohol stocks.
entries.deuterium_pyro: A favorite drink of ruffians, due to its terrible flavor and strong aftertaste.  You have to be tough to put down a Deuterium-pyro.
entries.deneelian_fizz_pudding: A rare pudding treat that crackles and pops as you eat it.
entries.crispic: A fried snack roll...commonly found in cantinas.
entries.crash_n_burn: A rare chemical mix of stimulant and depressive, Crash n' Burn heightens the user's awareness while at the same time increasing latent psychodepressive tendencies.
entries.cortyg: A strong alcohol produced by Wookiees.
entries.corellian_spiced_ale: A bottle of Corellian Spiced Ale.
entries.corellian_double_brandy: A bottle of Corellian Double Brandy.
entries.corellian_brandy: There is no brandy more flavorful and savory than Corellian Brandy.  Must be made with real Corellian fruits...otherwise it's just brandy.
entries.corellian_ale: Probably the most common alcoholic beverage in the galaxy.  Corellian Ale has a sweet flavor and a medium weight body.
entries.citros_snow_cake: A delicious pastry made with light fruits and sweet cake mix.
entries.cho_nor_hoola: A vile smelling stew favored by members of the Hutt race.  Only those with willpower can stand to eat a full serving of Cho-Nor-Hoola.
entries.charde: A refreshing beverage flavored with some unidentifiable organic substance.  Best served cold.
entries.chandad: A popular snack food filled with rice and fruit.
entries.caf: A stimulating beverage flavoured with grains or bean extract.
entries.breath_of_heaven_eff: Grants enhanced strength, quickness, and focus.
entries.breath_of_heaven: The Galaxy's most potent fire water: this stuff is as strong as it comes.
entries.braised_canron: A jellied meat carefully braised and seasoned.
entries.booster_blue: An out-of-use industrial dye employed in starship manufacturing that when consumed, enhances the user's physical reaction time.
entries.bofa_treat: A sweet, dried, fruit based snackfood.
entries.blue_milk: A protein enhanced milk beverage that has healing qualities.
entries.blood_chowder: A healthy meal made of soypro cooked in purified animal blood.
entries.blob_candy: A popular candy made from a filled blob of carbosyrup.
entries.blap_biscuit: A gooey biscuit served drenched in carbosyrup.
entries.bivoli_tempari: A very expensive and sweet dish that features toughened meat in a syrupy sauce.
entries.bio_up: You are under the effect of a positive biological effect.
entries.bio_kwi_adrenal_boost: A gland which secretes a fluid into the kwi bloodstream which increases their base regeneration in response to an attack.  Can cause burnout after the boost has run its course.
entries.bio_kliknik_fortitude_boost: An extract from the Kliknik immune system, this chemical coats the users organs with an ultra thin protective layer that insulates them during heavy exertion.  Can cause severe nausea when the body attempts to remove the coating.
entries.bio_down: You are under the effect of a negative biological effect.
entries.bespin_port: A sweet form of port native to Bespin.
entries.bantha_butter: Butter made from a Bantha's milk.
entries.bantha_blaster: A cantina favorite.  Drink with caution.
entries.antakarian_fire_dancer: A thick, potent ale made from alcoholic stock filtered through igneous rock and flavored with crushed gemstone.  This drink is popular with rough and tough types.
entries.aludium_pu36: A very pure and strong alcoholic stock popular during the Old Republic.  Aludium pu36 has a secret radioactive ingredient, but is safe enough for humanoid consumption.
entries.almond_kwevvu_crisp_munchies: A small pastry eaten by the handful.
entries.ale: A bottle of thick, foaming ale.
entries.alcohol: Basic alcohol stock made from some kind of cereal resource.
entries.aitha: A protein drink consumed by spacers to keep their bodies healthy during long runs.  Best served hot.
entries.ahrisa: A spicy food commonly found in cafes on Coruscant.
entries.accarragm_eff: Grants enhanced action, quickness, and stamina.
entries.accarragm: A strong Wookiee beverage made from fungus and alcohol stock.
